teaching in it.

00:15:21.340 --> 00:15:24.677
Christians have pulled these
Gospel--the details from the

00:15:24.677 --> 00:15:25.808
Gospels together.
 

00:15:25.808 --> 00:15:29.025
That's because John's the only
one that indicates that

00:15:29.025 --> 00:15:32.544
according to his reckoning
Jesus' ministry covered at least

00:15:32.544 --> 00:15:35.630
three Passovers,
the other Gospels don't have

00:15:35.630 --> 00:15:36.019
that.
 

00:15:36.019 --> 00:15:40.399
Jesus' parents and hometown
according to Matthew,

00:15:40.399 --> 00:15:44.139
Jesus' family is simply from
Bethlehem.

00:15:44.139 --> 00:15:46.518
That's where they start off,
that's where they end up,

00:15:46.518 --> 00:15:48.941
so Jesus' family is from
Bethlehem, Jesus later goes to

00:15:48.941 --> 00:15:49.480
Galilee.
 

00:15:49.480 --> 00:15:53.246
According to the Gospel of
Luke, Jesus' family is from

00:15:53.246 --> 00:15:56.355
Galilee,
they go to Bethlehem only for

00:15:56.355 --> 00:15:59.284
the census,
and then a month or so after

00:15:59.284 --> 00:16:01.710
the birth they go back to
Galilee,

00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:03.308
