there.

00:16:03.308 --> 00:16:05.932
Matthew simply has Jesus'
family from Judea in the

00:16:05.932 --> 00:16:08.984
beginning, and they end up
moving to Galilee after they go

00:16:08.984 --> 00:16:09.678
to Egypt.
 

00:16:09.678 --> 00:16:12.298
Luke has them from Galilee,
go to Judea,

00:16:12.298 --> 00:16:13.710
go back to Galilee.
 

00:16:13.710 --> 00:16:17.389
John doesn't have anything
about this Bethlehem birth.

00:16:17.389 --> 00:16:22.417
In fact he has--in 7:31 people
say, "How can you be the

00:16:22.417 --> 00:16:23.269
Messiah?
 

00:16:23.269 --> 00:16:25.980
Who says the Messiah is
